<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bù yào wèn wǒ 迦南243</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bù yào wèn wǒ shì fǒu kū guò
 bù yào wèn wǒ wèi le shén me
 bù yào wèn wǒ shì fǒu xiǎng jiā
 shì fǒu hái jì qǐ gù xiāng de xiǎo hé
 wǒ zhǐ jì dé yé sū shuō guò
 tā yǐ yǒng yuǎn de ài ài wǒ
 wǒ zhǐ zhī dào zhǔ shì hǎo mù rén
 wèi wǒ shě mìng wǒ yào wèi zhǔ huó.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>243</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>